Knattspyrnudeild Keflavíkur Mobile Application Development License

Introduction
This document outlines the licensing terms for the development of the Knattspyrnudeild Keflavíkur Mobile Application (the "Application") hosted on this GitHub repository. The intent is to foster community contributions to the Application's development while ensuring that the final product's use remains exclusive to Knattspyrnudeild Keflavíkur and its members, excluding competitive soccer clubs.

1. Grant of License for Development
Subject to the terms and conditions of this License, contributors are granted a non-exclusive, worldwide, royalty-free license to use, reproduce, modify, make derivative works of, and contribute to the Application in this repository for the sole purpose of contributing to the Application’s development.

2. Restrictions
a. Contributors must not use, distribute, or contribute to the Application with the intent to facilitate use by any soccer clubs participating in competitions deemed competitive to Knattspyrnudeild Keflavíkur.
b. Any contributions to the Application are subject to approval and integration by the project maintainers, who reserve the right to determine the suitability of all contributions to the Application’s goals and usage policies.

3. Ownership and Intellectual Property
a. All contributions to the Application shall be under the same terms as this License, without any additional terms or conditions.
b. Contributors agree to grant Knattspyrnudeild Keflavíkur a perpetual, worldwide, non-exclusive, royalty-free license to use, reproduce, modify, publish, distribute, and make derivative works of their contributions within the scope of the Application’s intended use.

4. No Endorsement
Contribution to the Application does not constitute an endorsement of the final product or its intended use by contributors.

5. Disclaimer
The Application is provided "as is", without warranty of any kind, express or implied. In no event shall the contributors or copyright holders be liable for any claim, damages, or other liability arising from the use or inability to use the Application.

6. Governing Law
This License and the contributions to the Application are governed by the laws of Iceland, without regard to its conflict of law principles.

Conclusion
By contributing to the Knattspyrnudeild Keflavíkur Mobile Application, contributors accept and agree to be bound by the terms and conditions of this License.